| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1105 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4562f443-8e0c-5e3e-8cc1-7a26b9e63211"
